{"tid":1721130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我代涉嫌偷竊可樂的警員鄭重道歉","createTime":"2019-11-14T14:43:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T16:50:07.000Z","uid":151324,"like":86,"dislike":148,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"80966140458024f19127dd47e75259404bace62c","tid":1721130,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:43:06.000Z","msg":"我代涉嫌偷竊可樂的警員鄭重道歉<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">最近網絡流傳一幅警員手拿紅色罐裝物的照片，有不少市民質疑該警員於執行職務其間偷竊可樂。警方曾於「記者招待會」澄清該名警員並沒有偷竊，說他手持的是小型滅火筒。然而這答案卻未令市民信服。<br />\n<br />\n今天「優品360」公開11月9日晚上元朗分店的CCTV，從片段清晰可見，該紅色物體實為滅火筒。(連結︰<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1402531283309224/posts/2513775302184811?vh=e&amp;d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1402531283309224%2Fposts%2F2513775302184811%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc63lPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=038a8192\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1402531283309224/posts/2513775302184811?vh=e&amp;d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>)</span><br />\n<br />\n在此我們代之前所有警員作出的暴徒行為鄭重致歉，唔係我們濫捕，亂打市民既話，就唔會有市民質疑我們。<br />\n<br />\n此外，我們感謝「優品360」公開CCTV片段，讓市民大眾得以看見警黑合作的真相<br />\n<br />\n近日社會嚴重撕裂，警民關係陷入深淵。警方濫用警權，藉執法之名，不合理地使用暴力對待市民。這些都在新聞片段中清晰可見。然而警方經常在其「記者招待會」以荒謬的言論為違規警察開脫罪名，導致警察公信力跌至谷底。需知道，一滴污水已經能夠污染一杯清水，市民不相信警方言論，並非沒有原因。<br />\n我們相信樹大有枯枝，我們相信警隊中大部份都是唔守紀律、打市民的黑警。由於大部分違規的警員，導致市民對警隊整體的不信任，實屬不幸。<br />\n這次事件讓我們明白到認清真相的重要。如果市民有公正可信的渠道投訴違規警員，相信警隊的威信很快便能夠重新建立。由此可見，成立獨立調查委員會實為化解警民敵對關係的最好方法。<br />\n<br />\n我們再次向各位市民鄭重道歉！有時行動打錯左你，對唔住！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港！時代革命！<br />\n五大訴求！缺一不可！<br />\n警察家屬敬啟<br />\n<br />\n聽日繼續三罷！"},{"pid":"66ac8ed66ea3632cabca744c170e5a4cf3c45c27","tid":1721130,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:43:59.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4ed4fce69f74f37a85a53440315a193188030c4f","tid":1721130,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b22d5d649985d7f3f0e4b2bc3e9eed0948bf51","tid":1721130,"uid":245552,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:47:00.000Z","msg":"幾時代警甴宣布接受制裁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5bb44c7eece9c0ed48062407a006da8b50c38f","tid":1721130,"uid":132128,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:47:29.000Z","msg":"道你老母"},{"pid":"640b2b753f980ffefa488621719090ca5b3ecd9f","tid":1721130,"uid":226959,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:47:55.000Z","msg":"道你老母"},{"pid":"3bf499010d05016c00e971d2308f66dca5fdee6c","tid":1721130,"uid":189068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:48:10.000Z","msg":"屌 唔記得睇user name"},{"pid":"879e31e98f11490d96fdcf53b81c85bed7ab598e","tid":1721130,"uid":40348,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:48:19.000Z","msg":"道你老母咩"},{"pid":"eba86620fb915838975b9d077b8174d3d9cbabcf","tid":1721130,"uid":23878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:48:48.000Z","msg":"同曱甴講人話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e63844cfed670b69db40b703e66321fdcf390253","tid":1721130,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c5bb44c7eece9c0ed48062407a006da8b50c38f","tid":1721130,"uid":132128,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:47:29.000Z","msg":"道你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:49:02.000Z","msg":"睇真d篇文"},{"pid":"0b996843529df390593796f2